comments: After Anthony (ORL) releases away from Clarkson (UTA) as he crosses midcourt, marginal arm to arm contact occurs.
Anthony (ORL) releases away from Clarkson (UTA) as he comes across midcourt and the contact that occurs is marginal.
Collins (UTA) contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Anthony (ORL) is late to the spot and initiates body contact to Clarkson (UTA) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Suggs (ORL) establishes himself in Collins' (UTA) path and firms up to absorb the contact as the pick is set.
Olynyk (UTA) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Banchero (ORL) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Carter Jr. (ORL) contests Markkanen's (UTA) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Carter Jr. (ORL) extends two hands into Horton-Tucker (UTA) during the back-screen without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Banchero (ORL) legally contests Collins' (UTA) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Following the defensive switch, Markkanen (UTA) and Anthony (ORL) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Collins (UTA) moves alongside Banchero's (ORL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) establishes himself in Isaac's (ORL) path and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Suggs (ORL) legally contests Horton-Tucker's (UTA) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Olynyk (UTA) commits a take foul on Carter Jr. (ORL) as he grabs the rebound.
